The use of machine learning also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the control system for the nano-landers, which falls under the category of control engineering (cs.SY) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the design and selection of the nano-landers, which falls under the category of computer engineering (cs.CE).
